    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="content-box">
            <div class="welcome-section">
                <div class="welcome-text">
                    <p class="welcome-top">Welcome to</p>
                    <p class="welcome-bottom">E-SHIFT</p>
                </div>
                <img src="~/images/logo.png" alt="E-SHIFT Logo" class="eshift-logo" />
            </div>
            <p class="intro-text">
                No matter the size scope of your move, with 20+ years experience in the mobility industry,
                E-Shift Relocations (Thailand) accommodates any move that is needed by clients.
            </p>
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="#" class="action-btn learn-more-btn">Learn More</a>
