</section>
</section>

<!-- About Our Agent -->
<section class="about-agent">
    <div class="about-content">
        <div class="about-left">
            <h2>About Our Agent</h2>
            <img src="~/images/agent-photo.jpg" alt="Our Agent">
        </div>
        <div class="about-right">
            <p>
                As a leading moving company in Bangkok, we believe that excellent customer service should be at the forefront of all operations, from the physical aspect of actually moving your possessions or business inventory from point A to point B to the ongoing support during your move. Moving from city to city in Thailand, overseas relocation, and factory/industry moves are all within our remit and we aim to make the process as stress-free as possible from start to finish. If you are planning any type of move imminently or in the future, our experienced moving service in Bangkok is more than ready to meet your requirements. Get in touch today for an initial consultation with one of our expert removalists in Bangkok.
            </p>
            <a href="#" class="quote-btn">Get a Quote</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Decorative Line -->
<div class="section-divider2"></div>
</section>
</section>

<section class="contact-section">
    <div class="contact-container">
        <!-- Left Side -->
        <div class="contact-left">
            <h2>Contact E-SHIFT Relocations (Thailand)</h2>
            <p>
                If you have any questions or concerns regarding a current or upcoming move with us, then please contact us at your earliest convenience using any of our many means for communication. Of course, our doors are always open to you; all you have to do is walk in.
            </p>
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> eshift.com</p>
                <p><strong>Branch Manager:</strong> gm@eshift.com</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Side -->
        <div class="contact-right">
            <form action="#" method="post">
                <div class="form-row">
                    <input type="text" name="fullname" placeholder="Full Name" required>
                    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-row">
                    <input type="text" name="subject" placeholder="Subject" required>
                    <input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="Phone Number" required>
                </div>
                <textarea name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Message" required></textarea>
                <button type="submit" class="contact-btn">Send Message</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


